# List of username/passwords pairs. Don't use whitespaces.
#
# credentials=admin:s3cr3t,user1:abc

# Dataset configuration. Starting with dataset., the second part determines
# the dataset name and the third part the role. The value lists the names of users
# that are assigned the specified permission grade.
# Don't use whitespaces.
# 
# One can create as many dataset groups as one wants.
# Currently there exist the permission grades **editor** and **reader** where the editor
# includes the reader permisssion so an editor can automatically do everything a reader can do.
# Make sure the user also are granted general access by beeing listed under credentials.
#
# dataset.dataset1.editor=user1
# dataset.dataset1.reader=user2
